    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Operationalize Four Peace Centers\r\n\t\r\n\t\tRaise awareness on peace related issues of PVSEs\r\n\t\r\n\t\tCapacity building of Peace Ambassadors and pressure groups of PVSEs\r\n\t\r\n\t\tTrain Para-psychosocial counselors, mediators and community journalists\r\n\t\r\n\t\tProvide support to community peace groups and Peace Ambassadors  to conduct different peace initiatives (including normalization activities and peace support) \r\n\t\r\n\t\tProvide support to advocacy initiatives of local peace committee\r\n\t\r\n\t\tBuilding of capacity and sharing of knowledge at institutional level\r\n\t\r\n\t\tRaise awareness of media on issues related to conflict-affected PVSEs\r\n\t\r\n\t\tPromote innovative peace initiatives of PVSEs\r\n\t\r\n\t\tDocument and disseminate success stories of PVSEs\r\n\t\r\n\t\tEstablish micro – macro linkages for policy dialogues\r\n\t\r\n\t\tProvide Support to peace building advocacy initiatives at national level\r\n\t\r\n\t\tEngage with political parties."
      },
